Student takes part in different projects or programmes or events connected to the pre-innovation phase of entrepreneurship. Student understands the processes of pre-innovation phase and knows how to use the knowledge in practice in already existing company's projects or StartUp's.Objectives/eesmärkid:  The aim of the course is to develop the knowledge of pre-innovation phase of entrepreneurship through practice and
to develop the skills for generating a business idea and planning business activities through practical exercises.Learning outcomes/õpiväljund:  After completing the course the student - can use the knowledge of planning business activities in practice - knows the steps of generating the business idea -can write a business plan - can present a business case or idea (pitching).
